articles.title: About this site
articles.description: Some additional details about the website
articles.contents:
About Me
My name is Miriam Heiss and I play the Organ. I am
Homeschooled, and enjoy making soap!
About the Project
My project, Taylor Swift and Bach will be comparing Taylor
Swift and Bach on things like song length, tempo, energy, and key. I got
the data from Spotify, but this is not the website it
will be on. The actual project will be here.
Goals
My project should show that classical music is not boring, and is
just as good as popular music.
This will be difficult, as classical music is slower and less
energetic (on average) than popular music.

I want my project to be informative about both popular and classical
music.
“This is data science” ~ Preceptor
Kane’s Free High
School Data Science Bootcamp
